Summary of what shipped on phase 1b:

- `src/ui/color.ts` (new) — semantic role helper exposing `error / success / warning / info / hint / bold / dimInfo`, `stripAnsi`, `clearLineSequence`. Honors `NO_COLOR` and per-stream TTY state; output is byte-identical when colors are stripped.
- `src/ui/spinner.ts`, `transcript.ts`, `output.ts` — refactored to route every escape sequence through the helper. Zero raw ANSI literals remain in any of `{spinner, logger, output, prompt, summary, transcript}.ts`.
- `src/engine/detect/index.ts` (new) — async `detect(cwd, opts?)` returning the exact `DetectionReport` interface the spec requires; deterministic, sub-second, fail-soft on missing/malformed `package.json`.
- `test/fixtures/` (new) — five fixture projects (react+vite+design.md, pure-node, pure-html, vue+vite, monorepo-root); `.fallowrc.json` adds them as entry points.
- `src/ui/preflight.ts` (new) — three-line summary in the exact constraints.md format (bold labels, dim values, dim-cyan arrow, no Unicode box-drawing); waits on Enter in TTY interactive mode, auto-proceeds with the CI suffix otherwise, skipped by `--yes`.
- `src/cli.ts` — `runPreflightGuard()` + `withConfigAndPreflight` wired into the ten pipeline-entry commands (default-create / shape / design / spec / research / refine / plan / build / rewind / retrospective). `catalog`, `dry-run`, `clean`, `check` deliberately bypass preflight.
- New test files: `color.test.ts` (15), `no-raw-ansi.test.ts` (7), `detect.test.ts` (16), `preflight.test.ts` (18), `cli.preflight-wiring.test.ts` (14), `cli.preflight-order.test.ts` (2). Net +73 passing tests, zero new failures.

